==English==
===Noun===
# {{mathematics}} The [[set]] of numbers that can be expressed as a [[ratio]] of [[integer]]s ([[fraction]]) <sup>m</sup>/<sub>n</sub>, where ''n'' is not zero. In [[set-builder notation]], it is defined as [[ℚ]]={<sup>m</sup>/</sub>n</sub>|m[[∈]][[ℤ]],n[[∈]][[ℕ]]}.

